ğŸŸ¢ 1. Initialize

This step figures out whatâ€™s happening:
	â€¢	Is this a pull request (PR), or a merge into the main branch?
	â€¢	It checks out your code from Git.
	â€¢	Finds the project name from a file called pom.xml.
	â€¢	If itâ€™s a special ITX project, it also pulls in extra files required for building.

